  "detailed_description": "Drawing inspirations from light gun shooter arcade cabinets, <i>Raygun Commando 2</i> is an on-rail reaction shooter in VR:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> features fast pace actions in exciting scenarios<br></li><li> Oculus/WMR friendly design by minimizing unnecessary turning/head re-orienting<br></li><li> physical room-scale locomotion only. Easy to jump into</li></ul>Fans who enjoyed the first game should find this sequel interesting",
